1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 24 =

20
00:01:51,340 --> 00:01:54,700
= Feng Shiyuan,
Chief Guard of Kaifeng Municipal Government =

21
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:57,980
Isn’t...isn’t this

22
00:01:57,980 --> 00:02:00,820
Chief Guard Feng of Kaifeng Municipal Government?

23
00:02:01,660 --> 00:02:03,100
Isn’t he a powerful figure?

24
00:02:03,340 --> 00:02:04,340
I know, right?

25
00:02:04,980 --> 00:02:06,180
It’s said Li’s wood store

26
00:02:06,900 --> 00:02:08,540
is backed by him.

27
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:10,060
That’s why it has easier access

28
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:11,620
to the supply and transportation of goods.

29
00:02:12,540 --> 00:02:14,460
More importantly, they can find buyers easily.

30
00:02:15,500 --> 00:02:16,620
What crime did he commit

31
00:02:17,100 --> 00:02:18,180
that he was beaten 50 times

32
00:02:18,300 --> 00:02:19,420
and exiled to Shaji Island?

33
00:02:20,500 --> 00:02:21,780
Don’t know.

34
00:02:27,580 --> 00:02:28,940
This Daily Political Report

35
00:02:29,460 --> 00:02:31,100
was bought from Xu’s Publishing House

36
00:02:31,460 --> 00:02:32,700
near the Great Xiangguo temple.

37
00:02:33,700 --> 00:02:34,780
It’s 12 coppers.

38
00:02:36,980 --> 00:02:39,940
This Summary of Office Reports

39
00:02:40,140 --> 00:02:43,780
is from Lu’s Bookstore near the dock.

40
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:47,180
The ink is even and it’s 14 coppers.

41
00:02:52,100 --> 00:02:53,860
People in the city

42
00:02:53,980 --> 00:02:55,940
can read reports of state affairs every day

43
00:02:55,940 --> 00:02:57,100
from different sources.

44
00:02:59,780 --> 00:03:01,620
After investigating Feng Shiyuan for over a year,

45
00:03:02,220 --> 00:03:03,860
almost the entire guarding branch of Kaifeng

46
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:06,260
is found guilty of bribery and corruption,

47
00:03:06,380 --> 00:03:08,940
and so are Assistant Administrator Cheng Lin

48
00:03:08,980 --> 00:03:10,420
and Chief of Privy Council Sheng Du.

49
00:03:14,540 --> 00:03:15,260
Here

50
00:03:16,460 --> 00:03:17,300
it says

51
00:03:17,300 --> 00:03:18,580
some sold by the human trafficker

52
00:03:18,780 --> 00:03:20,100
are descendants of the royal family

53
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:20,980
which offended

54
00:03:20,980 --> 00:03:22,140
and infuriated me.

55
00:03:35,980 --> 00:03:37,460
Commoners’ speculations

56
00:03:37,460 --> 00:03:39,260
of the palace and the court

57
00:03:39,260 --> 00:03:40,460
never end.

58
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:43,860
Where there are demands, there are supplies.

59
00:03:44,500 --> 00:03:45,860
Everyone discusses state affairs freely

60
00:03:46,540 --> 00:03:48,540
at restaurants and tea houses.

61
00:03:48,780 --> 00:03:51,220
What they say is 20% true at most.

62
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,660
It’s as wild as fantasy stories,

63
00:03:54,460 --> 00:03:56,940
which involves high-ranking officials

64
00:03:57,100 --> 00:03:58,660
and private affairs.

65
00:03:58,660 --> 00:04:00,060
So disrespectful.

66
00:04:00,860 --> 00:04:02,740
If we can make

67
00:04:03,340 --> 00:04:04,420
state reports public,

68
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:08,020
it’ll correct some rumors

69
00:04:08,020 --> 00:04:10,500
if not all.

70
00:04:10,900 --> 00:04:12,260
At least, the authenticity can be increased

71
00:04:12,260 --> 00:04:13,540
from 20% to 50%.

72
00:04:27,540 --> 00:04:28,740
I’m concerned

73
00:04:29,020 --> 00:04:30,340
that if rumors are wild spread

74
00:04:30,340 --> 00:04:31,580
and regarded as the truth,

75
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:33,100
the public might be misled.

76
00:04:34,980 --> 00:04:37,580
Rumors can never be the truth

77
00:04:37,980 --> 00:04:39,580
unless someone manipulates public opinions.

78
00:04:40,780 --> 00:04:42,660
People chat all the time.

79
00:04:42,940 --> 00:04:44,420
They all have

80
00:04:44,780 --> 00:04:46,340
their sides of the stories.

81
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:47,620
As long as they don’t affect

82
00:04:47,620 --> 00:04:49,300
people’s livelihood,

83
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:51,620
marriages, funerals and careers,

84
00:04:52,100 --> 00:04:53,020
their passion

85
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:54,980
will soon wear off.

86
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:57,300
I bet

87
00:04:57,780 --> 00:05:00,100
before Feng Shiyuan arrives at Shaji Island,

88
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:02,740
someone else will replace him

89
00:05:02,980 --> 00:05:04,260
to be the center of the discussions.

90
00:05:04,660 --> 00:05:05,740
There’s no need

91
00:05:06,060 --> 00:05:07,860
to bother yourself

92
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:09,460
with their free talks.

93
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:21,860
Fine. Alright.

94
00:05:22,420 --> 00:05:23,260
I admit

95
00:05:25,180 --> 00:05:27,420
I chose to come to the city center today

96
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:28,780
when Feng Shiyuan was about to be exiled

97
00:05:29,060 --> 00:05:31,020
to hear people’s opinions.

98
00:05:31,980 --> 00:05:34,140
So much effort was put into this case

99
00:05:34,140 --> 00:05:35,180
to make sure

100
00:05:35,180 --> 00:05:36,660
that culprits would all be brought to justice.

101
00:05:37,340 --> 00:05:39,420
I was kind of expecting to be praised

102
00:05:40,500 --> 00:05:42,860
yet they didn’t seem

103
00:05:43,260 --> 00:05:44,660
to appreciate my effort.

104
00:05:55,260 --> 00:05:56,020
Never mind.

105
00:05:56,900 --> 00:05:58,220
Their discussions

106
00:05:58,580 --> 00:06:00,020
aren’t based on the whole truth

107
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:00,980
or the whole picture.

108
00:06:01,940 --> 00:06:03,380
No knowledge, no truth.

109
00:06:03,980 --> 00:06:06,300
But I can’t

110
00:06:06,540 --> 00:06:08,300
reveal every detail

111
00:06:08,380 --> 00:06:10,140
to the public.

112
00:06:13,300 --> 00:06:14,940
Your Majesty is insightful.

113
00:06:20,140 --> 00:06:21,620
Ignore those noises.

114
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:23,060
The most horrific finding

115
00:06:23,420 --> 00:06:24,700
from Feng Shiyuan’s case

116
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:26,580
is that

117
00:06:26,620 --> 00:06:28,420
those chained officials

118
00:06:28,780 --> 00:06:30,540
used to build a wide net across Kaifeng,

119
00:06:30,900 --> 00:06:33,220
making the city under their control.

120
00:06:33,340 --> 00:06:34,940
Think about how many officials we have

121
00:06:34,940 --> 00:06:36,300
in the other 18 provinces.

122
00:06:36,940 --> 00:06:38,260
Don’t they control

123
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:40,180
the fate of our entire state?

124
00:06:42,140 --> 00:06:47,260
= 1041 A.D. =

125
00:06:48,900 --> 00:06:50,660
She was sleeping soundly in my arms.

126
00:06:51,180 --> 00:06:52,660
How come right after I gave her to you,

127
00:06:53,020 --> 00:06:53,980
she woke up?

128
00:06:54,700 --> 00:06:55,980
Don’t touch her ever again.

129
00:07:04,660 --> 00:07:05,980
Lady of Qinghe County,

130
00:07:06,380 --> 00:07:07,020
no,

131
00:07:07,100 --> 00:07:08,700
it’s Lady Zhang now.

132
00:07:08,980 --> 00:07:09,820
She’s rising

133
00:07:10,340 --> 00:07:11,940
= Zhang Chengzhao Liang Huaiji =
after giving birth to a girl.

134
00:07:12,140 --> 00:07:13,460
If she has a boy in the future...

135
00:07:16,060 --> 00:07:17,380
Why don’t you want to serve her?

136
00:07:17,660 --> 00:07:19,860
It’s a chance of a lifetime.

137
00:07:22,220 --> 00:07:24,020
I wasn’t told to be transferred there.

138
00:07:24,260 --> 00:07:25,180
Stop pretending.

139
00:07:25,580 --> 00:07:27,540
My source is absolutely reliable.

140
00:07:28,740 --> 00:07:30,860
Why don’t you want to be there?

141
00:07:31,980 --> 00:07:32,980
Is it because she’s too arrogant?

142
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:35,460
Well, I’m fine with that.

143
00:07:35,900 --> 00:07:37,780
The more arrogant women seem,

144
00:07:37,860 --> 00:07:38,780
the easier they can be comforted.

145
00:07:40,420 --> 00:07:42,140
I love staying at the Imperial Academy.

146
00:07:42,780 --> 00:07:44,100
You’re on Zhang Maoze’s side.

147
00:07:44,940 --> 00:07:46,220
He listens to the Empress,

148
00:07:46,220 --> 00:07:47,780
so that makes Lady Zhang his opponent.

149
00:07:51,740 --> 00:07:52,420
I see.

150
00:07:53,220 --> 00:07:54,860
Although Zhang Maoze is young,

151
00:07:55,020 --> 00:07:56,580
he practically grew up

152
00:07:56,940 --> 00:07:58,700
with His Majesty in the palace

153
00:07:58,980 --> 00:08:00,420
and is his most trusted man.

154
00:08:01,140 --> 00:08:03,060
His power and influence

155
00:08:03,540 --> 00:08:04,980
are even bigger and wider than Deputy Officer.

156
00:08:05,740 --> 00:08:09,220
= The Third Princess Zhao Chuyue =

157
00:08:16,980 --> 00:08:18,580
Why are you still sitting here

158
00:08:18,900 --> 00:08:20,340
instead of going back to sleep?

159
00:08:21,580 --> 00:08:22,420
What’s wrong?

160
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:24,580
Aunt,

161
00:08:26,700 --> 00:08:28,020
is Chuyue getting better?

162
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:30,220
Is her fever gone?

163
00:08:31,100 --> 00:08:32,940
Not yet.

164
00:08:33,380 --> 00:08:34,340
She already

165
00:08:34,340 --> 00:08:35,380
took the medicine

166
00:08:35,380 --> 00:08:36,340
and is no longer vomiting.

167
00:08:37,140 --> 00:08:38,620
Look at you.

168
00:08:38,620 --> 00:08:39,700
You’re ill yourself.

169
00:08:39,900 --> 00:08:41,260
It’s cold and windy here.

170
00:08:41,300 --> 00:08:42,900
Go back to your room now.

171
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:45,260
I want to be close to my daughter

172
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:48,740
so that I won’t miss anything.

173
00:08:50,860 --> 00:08:51,660
Listen,

174
00:08:52,540 --> 00:08:55,140
you should take care of yourself first.

175
00:08:56,900 --> 00:08:58,260
Your daughter needs you.

176
00:08:59,100 --> 00:09:00,780
If anything happens to you,

177
00:09:01,500 --> 00:09:03,140
Chuyue will be on her own.

178
00:09:03,380 --> 00:09:04,660
Who else can she depend on?

179
00:09:08,980 --> 00:09:10,900
Her father is the Emperor.

180
00:09:12,820 --> 00:09:14,420
Who dares to mistreat her?

181
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,300
Aunt,

182
00:09:21,260 --> 00:09:22,100
is it possible

183
00:09:24,180 --> 00:09:25,300
that someone plots

184
00:09:25,300 --> 00:09:26,580
to harm my daughter?

185
00:09:27,540 --> 00:09:28,940
She was weak

186
00:09:28,940 --> 00:09:30,100
when I was pregnant.

187
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:32,340
Then she became stronger

188
00:09:32,500 --> 00:09:34,380
and came out healthy.

189
00:09:35,220 --> 00:09:36,540
But right after that,

190
00:09:36,980 --> 00:09:38,540
her condition is worsening.

191
00:09:38,860 --> 00:09:40,460
Which heartless animal

192
00:09:40,460 --> 00:09:41,500
is hurting my baby?

193
00:09:42,060 --> 00:09:43,780
He...he can come to me.

194
00:09:48,060 --> 00:09:49,340
Babies at this age

195
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:50,820
are fragile.

196
00:09:52,260 --> 00:09:53,500
Don’t think too much.

197
00:09:54,460 --> 00:09:55,620
Really?

198
00:09:56,660 --> 00:09:58,500
How come Huirou is never sick?

199
00:10:00,380 --> 00:10:01,340
I’ve asked around.

200
00:10:02,020 --> 00:10:03,620
Since she was born,

201
00:10:04,140 --> 00:10:05,660
she’s been eating and sleeping well

202
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:07,020
without falling ill for once.

203
00:10:07,540 --> 00:10:09,180
Clearly, the Empress is protecting her.

204
00:10:13,500 --> 00:10:14,900
Now, I finally realize

205
00:10:15,900 --> 00:10:19,060
that the one ruling this harem

206
00:10:20,100 --> 00:10:21,980
isn’t His Majesty but the Empress.

207
00:10:30,060 --> 00:10:32,020
Taotao has grown up.

208
00:10:34,340 --> 00:10:37,340
Huirou is almost four years old.

209
00:10:39,380 --> 00:10:42,260
I still remember she was so soft and little

210
00:10:42,260 --> 00:10:43,980
in my arms when she was a baby.

211
00:10:45,340 --> 00:10:47,020
You can soon

212
00:10:47,020 --> 00:10:48,740
hold another one in your arms.

213
00:10:55,500 --> 00:10:57,460
I hope it’s a boy

214
00:10:59,460 --> 00:11:01,060
not because I have wild ambition.

215
00:11:02,060 --> 00:11:04,300
I can only say this to you

216
00:11:04,700 --> 00:11:06,300
without being called mendacious.

217
00:11:08,340 --> 00:11:11,020
When Madam Zhang was in labor,

218
00:11:11,300 --> 00:11:12,420
I prayed secretly

219
00:11:13,220 --> 00:11:14,860
that she’d give birth to a boy.

220
00:11:15,620 --> 00:11:16,540
Unfortunately...

221
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:18,980
I know you aren’t mendacious.

222
00:11:19,860 --> 00:11:21,460
I think I know better than His Majesty

223
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:24,500
how much you care about him.

224
00:11:28,900 --> 00:11:30,580
I grew up with him.

225
00:11:31,980 --> 00:11:33,180
According to my memory,

226
00:11:33,700 --> 00:11:35,860
he was only truly happy twice.

227
00:11:36,780 --> 00:11:38,980
One was knowing I was pregnant with Huirou.

228
00:11:39,700 --> 00:11:42,060
The other was when he held her

229
00:11:42,460 --> 00:11:43,980
after she was born.

230
00:11:45,740 --> 00:11:48,900
This time, after learning

231
00:11:49,660 --> 00:11:50,820
that I was pregnant again,

232
00:11:51,300 --> 00:11:53,140
I noticed

233
00:11:54,300 --> 00:11:56,220
that he was more nervous than happy.

234
00:12:00,100 --> 00:12:02,100
He’s over 30 but still has no son.

235
00:12:03,300 --> 00:12:05,660
Of course he’s anxious.

236
00:12:07,620 --> 00:12:08,700
But things like this

237
00:12:09,060 --> 00:12:11,100
aren’t in our control.

238
00:12:13,660 --> 00:12:15,100
I understand you’re eager to help him,

239
00:12:15,700 --> 00:12:17,260
but if your health

240
00:12:17,260 --> 00:12:19,260
is affected by your anxiety,

241
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,020
he’ll become more worried than he already is.

242
00:12:23,460 --> 00:12:24,300
I know

243
00:12:25,020 --> 00:12:26,220
it’s easier said than done.

244
00:12:26,780 --> 00:12:28,220
Those involved in this,

245
00:12:28,380 --> 00:12:30,620
you, His Majesty

246
00:12:30,860 --> 00:12:33,180
and Madam Zhang can hardly do it.

247
00:12:35,340 --> 00:12:36,700
What you need to remember is

248
00:12:38,260 --> 00:12:39,460
that the more relaxed you are,

249
00:12:40,580 --> 00:12:42,180
the less worried he becomes.

250
00:12:42,180 --> 00:12:43,020
That’s it.

251
00:12:50,420 --> 00:12:51,420
Slowly.

252
00:12:51,820 --> 00:12:52,980
Your Highness, mother,

253
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:54,940
I can throw coins.

254
00:12:54,980 --> 00:12:55,940
Come here.

255
00:12:55,940 --> 00:12:57,100
I won these.

256
00:12:58,780 --> 00:13:01,020
= Princess Huirou =
You’re pregnant

257
00:13:01,020 --> 00:13:02,420
and can’t be exhausted.

258
00:13:05,780 --> 00:13:07,900
I’m a big girl now.

259
00:13:09,180 --> 00:13:10,540
These are my gifts

260
00:13:10,700 --> 00:13:12,660
for the baby.

261
00:13:13,100 --> 00:13:13,740
Good.

262
00:13:15,300 --> 00:13:16,420
You’re so sweet.

263
00:13:17,460 --> 00:13:18,140
Come here.

264
00:13:19,060 --> 00:13:20,460
A candied fruit for you.

265
00:13:23,660 --> 00:13:24,420
Go play.

266
00:13:28,940 --> 00:13:30,700
The more you hate them,

267
00:13:32,180 --> 00:13:33,500
the calmer you have to be.

268
00:13:34,580 --> 00:13:37,860
More importantly, you can’t look hostile.

269
00:13:39,860 --> 00:13:41,620
They’re jealous of you

270
00:13:42,060 --> 00:13:43,420
and ganging up against you,

271
00:13:44,060 --> 00:13:45,260
but they mislead His Majesty to think

272
00:13:45,380 --> 00:13:48,100
they’re the victims.

273
00:13:49,980 --> 00:13:52,180
And they use Huirou

274
00:13:52,180 --> 00:13:53,420
to attract His Majesty’s attention.

275
00:13:53,900 --> 00:13:55,900
He loves his daughter,

276
00:13:56,460 --> 00:13:58,580
so he visits Madam Miao a lot to see her.

277
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:02,060
Madam Miao and the Empress

278
00:14:02,060 --> 00:14:03,780
are on the same side.

279
00:14:04,340 --> 00:14:05,300
What should I do?

280
00:14:06,980 --> 00:14:07,940
First,

281
00:14:09,340 --> 00:14:10,380
be humble.

282
00:14:11,860 --> 00:14:13,020
You can’t say

283
00:14:13,620 --> 00:14:15,460
how bad the Empress is

284
00:14:17,020 --> 00:14:18,340
but let His Majesty

285
00:14:19,140 --> 00:14:22,180
hear that

286
00:14:22,820 --> 00:14:24,260
from others.

287
00:14:27,820 --> 00:14:28,740
It’s been confirmed.

288
00:14:29,180 --> 00:14:30,820
Before Jia came to the palace,

289
00:14:31,180 --> 00:14:33,100
she engaged in salt smuggling

290
00:14:33,180 --> 00:14:34,340
and human trafficking in the west.

291
00:14:34,780 --> 00:14:36,500
She isn’t involved in Feng Shiyuan’s case

292
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:37,580
- but... - Don’t bring it up

293
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:39,220
outside this door.

294
00:14:39,660 --> 00:14:40,260
Why?

295
00:14:41,220 --> 00:14:42,740
You think that’s the only thing

296
00:14:43,500 --> 00:14:45,620
that His Majesty doesn’t like about her?

297
00:14:46,180 --> 00:14:47,500
You knew it already, Master?

298
00:14:49,140 --> 00:14:50,100
In your opinion,

299
00:14:50,980 --> 00:14:52,300
does His Majesty

300
00:14:52,540 --> 00:14:53,620
like this woman or not?

301
00:14:54,860 --> 00:14:55,940
He doesn’t,

302
00:14:56,620 --> 00:14:57,340
but

303
00:14:57,580 --> 00:14:59,660
Madam Zhang insisted on having her.

304
00:15:00,380 --> 00:15:01,820
Back then, there was no evidence against her,

305
00:15:02,140 --> 00:15:03,300
so His Majesty couldn’t do anything.

306
00:15:04,140 --> 00:15:06,100
Now, Madam Zhang relies on her even more.

307
00:15:06,260 --> 00:15:07,900
She needs her all the time.

308
00:15:08,260 --> 00:15:09,580
So His Majesty’s hands are tied.

309
00:15:10,180 --> 00:15:11,180
Would you rather see

310
00:15:11,380 --> 00:15:13,220
Madam Zhang move to His Majesty’s chamber again

311
00:15:13,220 --> 00:15:14,500
after losing her aunt?

312
00:15:15,180 --> 00:15:16,100
I actually think it’s not bad

313
00:15:16,580 --> 00:15:18,100
for Madam Zhang to have her around.

314
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:25,620
= Yan’an =

315
00:15:25,620 --> 00:15:27,900
= Yan’an Administrative Office =

316
00:15:28,500 --> 00:15:30,340
Captain Di, you must’ve gained tons of loot

317
00:15:30,500 --> 00:15:31,820
from the sneak attack.

318
00:15:32,860 --> 00:15:33,940
Stop framing me.

319
00:15:34,700 --> 00:15:36,900
Chief forbids us from killing the surrendered,

320
00:15:37,100 --> 00:15:38,540
hurting women and children of the Qiangs

321
00:15:38,660 --> 00:15:39,860
or taking their properties.

322
00:15:40,180 --> 00:15:41,260
I got nothing.

323
00:15:41,260 --> 00:15:42,180
Loot my foot.

324
00:15:48,380 --> 00:15:49,260
Chief Fan.

325
00:15:51,500 --> 00:15:53,700
Stew this for Chief.

326
00:15:53,700 --> 00:15:54,460
Yes.

327
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:02,180
We’ve regained Ansai and Wan’an.

328
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:03,940
Last month, General Ren Fu

329
00:16:04,020 --> 00:16:05,020
recaptured the Baibao.

330
00:16:05,580 --> 00:16:07,260
Invaders in Bao’an have also retreated.

331
00:16:08,460 --> 00:16:11,540
Now, with my victory at Luziping,

332
00:16:12,260 --> 00:16:13,500
when will we battle

333
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:14,340
Yuanhao’s main force?

334
00:16:14,740 --> 00:16:15,940
I, Di Qing, volunteer to be the vanguard.

335
00:16:18,580 --> 00:16:19,260
Vanguard?

336
00:16:23,020 --> 00:16:24,980
Who else is a better candidate than me?

337
00:16:28,340 --> 00:16:30,780
It’s not that you aren’t fit for that post

338
00:16:31,380 --> 00:16:32,420
but that post

339
00:16:33,020 --> 00:16:36,300
doesn’t fit you at the moment.

340
00:16:46,660 --> 00:16:47,980
= The Commentary of Zuo =

341
00:16:52,060 --> 00:16:55,180
Generals without understanding of history

342
00:16:55,220 --> 00:16:57,260
can only be regarded as foolhardy.

343
00:16:57,820 --> 00:16:59,220
You have a lot of potential

344
00:16:59,220 --> 00:17:01,860
and should study and think more

345
00:17:02,380 --> 00:17:06,860
so that you can become a pillar of our country.

346
00:17:08,020 --> 00:17:09,100
Really?

347
00:17:09,900 --> 00:17:10,700
I can fight

348
00:17:10,700 --> 00:17:11,820
on the battlefield fearlessly.

349
00:17:12,700 --> 00:17:13,980
Well, words in this book

350
00:17:14,660 --> 00:17:16,300
are strange to me.

351
00:17:16,620 --> 00:17:19,420
You can ask me

352
00:17:19,500 --> 00:17:20,460
for things you don’t know or understand.

353
00:17:21,340 --> 00:17:23,580
There are the talented and the mediocre

354
00:17:23,820 --> 00:17:25,820
but no one is born a scholar or a soldier.

355
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:30,500
Simply, some learn to read first

356
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:32,740
while others ride.

357
00:17:33,020 --> 00:17:35,300
Other than bravery,

358
00:17:35,820 --> 00:17:37,220
you own good judgment

359
00:17:37,700 --> 00:17:38,860
and an agile mind.

360
00:17:39,100 --> 00:17:40,940
You’re also kind to the old and weak.

361
00:17:41,900 --> 00:17:44,260
Why can’t a smart, brave and benevolent talent

362
00:17:44,500 --> 00:17:46,100
also be knowledgeable?

363
00:17:46,700 --> 00:17:47,580
Benevolent?

364
00:17:49,420 --> 00:17:51,220
After seizing Ansai and Wan’an,

365
00:17:51,980 --> 00:17:53,100
didn’t you

366
00:17:53,100 --> 00:17:54,540
disagree with them killing captives?

367
00:17:55,900 --> 00:17:57,180
I’ve been stationing here

368
00:17:57,180 --> 00:17:58,460
for a decade.

369
00:17:58,980 --> 00:18:00,260
When there was no war,

370
00:18:00,700 --> 00:18:01,660
I traded tea with them

371
00:18:01,660 --> 00:18:03,140
for salt.

372
00:18:03,500 --> 00:18:05,740
We used to hunt sheep and catch rabbits together.

373
00:18:06,620 --> 00:18:07,860
When wolves came,

374
00:18:07,900 --> 00:18:09,340
we worked together to kill them.

375
00:18:09,900 --> 00:18:10,940
Soldiers

376
00:18:10,940 --> 00:18:12,220
simply follow their superior’s orders.

377
00:18:12,700 --> 00:18:14,900
We just need to get back what we lost.

378
00:18:15,460 --> 00:18:17,100
Why kill others?

379
00:18:20,460 --> 00:18:21,940
That’s called benevolence.

380
00:18:28,100 --> 00:18:29,580
I’ve never attended school

381
00:18:30,100 --> 00:18:31,380
or called anyone teacher.

382
00:18:35,380 --> 00:18:36,420
From now on,

383
00:18:36,820 --> 00:18:38,500
I’ll regard you as my teacher

384
00:18:39,300 --> 00:18:40,140
and pay respects to you

385
00:18:40,180 --> 00:18:41,860
the same as I do

386
00:18:42,180 --> 00:18:43,020
to my parents.

387
00:18:51,900 --> 00:18:53,060
Please rise.

388
00:18:59,140 --> 00:19:02,420
I’m going to teach you a character now.

389
00:19:27,180 --> 00:19:28,100
This is “Wu”, meaning “force”.

390
00:19:28,980 --> 00:19:31,300
The two parts "Zhi” and “Ge” it is consisted of

391
00:19:31,940 --> 00:19:34,300
mean to stop the war.

392
00:19:34,900 --> 00:19:36,220
That tells us

393
00:19:36,700 --> 00:19:38,900
we risk our lives

394
00:19:38,900 --> 00:19:39,940
to safeguard our nation

395
00:19:40,300 --> 00:19:42,940
not to kill others for loot

396
00:19:43,940 --> 00:19:46,220
but to stop the war.

397
00:19:50,460 --> 00:19:51,780
I hope

398
00:19:52,860 --> 00:19:54,900
you can always think of this character

399
00:19:55,380 --> 00:19:56,820
whenever you wield your saber.

400
00:19:57,300 --> 00:20:01,060
Force is only used to stop the war.

401
00:20:07,420 --> 00:20:08,780
That rabbit

402
00:20:09,020 --> 00:20:10,980
has been stewed long enough.

403
00:20:11,820 --> 00:20:12,580
I remember

404
00:20:13,020 --> 00:20:14,940
Zhigui told me in his letter earlier

405
00:20:14,980 --> 00:20:17,580
that he’d come today to discuss strategies.

406
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:21,020
I bet he’ll bring us liquor.

407
00:20:23,700 --> 00:20:24,860
-Good! Yeah! - Go on!

408
00:20:24,860 --> 00:20:25,620
Zhigui,

409
00:20:26,980 --> 00:20:30,100
even if we spare no effort

410
00:20:30,780 --> 00:20:32,860
to break into Xixia

411
00:20:33,020 --> 00:20:35,580
and behead Yuanhao in public,

412
00:20:36,180 --> 00:20:36,860
then what?

413
00:20:37,700 --> 00:20:40,380
Assign our officials

414
00:20:40,580 --> 00:20:42,380
and Imperial Guards

415
00:20:42,700 --> 00:20:44,180
to govern regions of the Tanguts?

416
00:20:47,860 --> 00:20:48,540
Uh...

417
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:52,180
Even if we win,

418
00:20:52,740 --> 00:20:54,540
we’re shorthanded to guard those places for long.

419
00:20:54,900 --> 00:20:57,100
Few are used to the farming-grazing lifestyle

420
00:20:57,180 --> 00:20:58,700
or willing to move

421
00:20:58,700 --> 00:20:59,900
to the Tanguts’ land.

422
00:21:01,140 --> 00:21:03,580
His Majesty cares about the masses.

423
00:21:04,380 --> 00:21:07,580
He’d never sacrifice their welfare

424
00:21:07,820 --> 00:21:09,660
and drain their fortune

425
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:12,060
in exchange for a victory

426
00:21:12,060 --> 00:21:13,980
that can’t solve all the problems.

427
00:21:15,740 --> 00:21:17,260
There’s no need for such a huge sacrifice

428
00:21:17,980 --> 00:21:19,580
or crossing the border.

429
00:21:20,180 --> 00:21:21,940
With the army we have,

430
00:21:22,500 --> 00:21:23,740
don’t we have a chance

431
00:21:23,940 --> 00:21:25,380
to locate Yuanhao’s main force,

432
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:26,980
battle it head-on

433
00:21:27,180 --> 00:21:28,700
and clobber it

434
00:21:28,940 --> 00:21:29,980
so that we can turn the table?

435
00:21:30,260 --> 00:21:32,180
And then what?

436
00:21:33,300 --> 00:21:34,100
Negotiate for peace.

437
00:21:35,420 --> 00:21:37,220
Demand that Yuanhao abandon his title,

438
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:38,380
establish the border

439
00:21:38,620 --> 00:21:39,980
and sign the treaty

440
00:21:41,380 --> 00:21:42,140
to bring peace to people in Fuyan,

441
00:21:42,420 --> 00:21:44,340
= Yin Zhu, courtesy name Shilu =
Huan and Qing Counties.

442
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:47,260
Manage water, promote farming and education,

443
00:21:47,860 --> 00:21:48,940
reopen markets

444
00:21:49,500 --> 00:21:50,740
to make this border town

445
00:21:51,260 --> 00:21:52,700
as prosperous as the Capital.

446
00:21:53,180 --> 00:21:55,340
All that can be achieved

447
00:21:55,340 --> 00:21:56,540
without a massacre.

448
00:21:57,180 --> 00:21:59,060
We can build forts,

449
00:21:59,060 --> 00:22:00,860
enforce laws, open up wastelands to grow grains.

450
00:22:01,060 --> 00:22:02,900
Those forts can keep Yuanhao out.

451
00:22:03,380 --> 00:22:05,660
His cavalrymen are good at long-range raids,

452
00:22:05,940 --> 00:22:07,060
but if we battle head-on,

453
00:22:07,500 --> 00:22:09,540
they aren’t unable

454
00:22:09,580 --> 00:22:10,700
to pass our heavily-guarded forts.

455
00:22:11,700 --> 00:22:12,740
Compared with us,

456
00:22:12,740 --> 00:22:14,540
Yuanhao owns fewer supplies.

457
00:22:15,300 --> 00:22:16,620
As long as we hold our position,

458
00:22:17,380 --> 00:22:19,780
all his attempts will fail

459
00:22:20,420 --> 00:22:22,780
and eventually, he can’t afford the cost

460
00:22:22,780 --> 00:22:24,140
and will beg for a truce.

461
00:22:25,260 --> 00:22:27,140
Yuanhao is unruly,

462
00:22:27,820 --> 00:22:29,300
cunning and greedy.

463
00:22:30,300 --> 00:22:31,980
Will he ask for a truce

464
00:22:31,980 --> 00:22:33,740
out of concerns about his people?

465
00:22:33,860 --> 00:22:34,620
If not,

466
00:22:34,620 --> 00:22:36,460
the longer it goes, the less people have to live.

467
00:22:36,540 --> 00:22:38,020
He will be forced to take that step.

468
00:22:38,300 --> 00:22:41,540
But Xiwen, how long will that take?

469
00:22:42,180 --> 00:22:43,580
Our resources are abundant,

470
00:22:43,980 --> 00:22:46,180
troops are well-equipped,

471
00:22:46,420 --> 00:22:47,980
and we have fine horses.

472
00:22:48,460 --> 00:22:49,980
Do you think our soldiers

473
00:22:49,980 --> 00:22:50,980
are cowards

474
00:22:51,300 --> 00:22:52,540
who can only hide behind the forts

475
00:22:52,540 --> 00:22:54,060
instead of launching attacks?

476
00:22:54,180 --> 00:22:57,660
It’s easy to hold than to attack in this area.

477
00:22:58,620 --> 00:23:01,540
Previous battles have already proven that.

478
00:23:09,420 --> 00:23:10,620
During the war,

479
00:23:12,020 --> 00:23:14,140
winning and losing should be set aside.

480
00:23:16,140 --> 00:23:17,220
We’re talking about

481
00:23:17,220 --> 00:23:18,620
thousands of lives.

482
00:23:19,140 --> 00:23:20,940
How could we set them aside?

483
00:23:43,900 --> 00:23:45,460
Fan Zhongyan insists

484
00:23:46,580 --> 00:23:48,100
on defense

485
00:23:48,260 --> 00:23:50,620
while Han Qi proposes offense

486
00:23:50,620 --> 00:23:51,660
by locating Yuanhao’s main force

487
00:23:51,660 --> 00:23:52,740
and battle it head-on.

488
00:23:53,420 --> 00:23:54,780
They both have their reasons.

489
00:23:55,900 --> 00:23:56,780
I asked Xia Song

490
00:23:56,780 --> 00:23:57,940
to decide,

491
00:23:58,620 --> 00:23:59,620
yet he

492
00:23:59,620 --> 00:24:01,580
sent me all their reports

493
00:24:01,620 --> 00:24:03,620
and arguments,

494
00:24:03,660 --> 00:24:05,020
saying he was unable to decide.

495
00:24:05,620 --> 00:24:06,660
Chief Xia

496
00:24:06,940 --> 00:24:09,060
used to be against launching attacks.

497
00:24:11,540 --> 00:24:12,460
Perhaps

498
00:24:13,940 --> 00:24:15,500
during his time at the frontline,

499
00:24:15,860 --> 00:24:16,740
he reviewed

500
00:24:16,780 --> 00:24:18,060
the latest situation of both sides

501
00:24:18,620 --> 00:24:19,740
and his confidence grew.

502
00:24:23,940 --> 00:24:24,980
Over the years,

503
00:24:25,380 --> 00:24:27,420
Han and Fan have seldom disagreed with each other.

504
00:24:27,900 --> 00:24:29,420
Even when they were thousands of miles apart,

505
00:24:29,500 --> 00:24:30,420
their opinions

506
00:24:30,700 --> 00:24:31,420
on the same matter

507
00:24:31,420 --> 00:24:32,940
were almost identical.

508
00:24:35,060 --> 00:24:37,420
Han Qi respects Zhongyan a lot.

509
00:24:37,580 --> 00:24:38,500
But this time,

510
00:24:38,700 --> 00:24:40,420
he must’ve refuted his arguments

511
00:24:40,420 --> 00:24:41,980
for a reason.

512
00:24:46,860 --> 00:24:48,140
Fan Zhongyan is old.

513
00:24:48,780 --> 00:24:50,140
He’s become more prudent

514
00:24:50,420 --> 00:24:51,700
and less adventurous.

515
00:24:52,300 --> 00:24:53,700
Were it 20 years ago,

516
00:24:54,300 --> 00:24:56,980
perhaps he’d be prone to offense

517
00:24:57,220 --> 00:24:58,740
more than Han Qi.

518
00:25:02,160 --> 00:25:10,577
♪ Scenes change on the frontier in autumn ♪

519
00:25:11,913 --> 00:25:21,500
♪ Wild geese leave without adieu ♪

520
00:25:21,500 --> 00:25:29,721
♪ Shouts echo on all sides when the bugle blows ♪

521
00:25:29,777 --> 00:25:43,980
♪ Amid the mountains the sun sets,
the city is closed ♪

522
00:25:55,050 --> 00:26:04,281
♪ A toast to home far away ♪

523
00:26:04,706 --> 00:26:14,140
♪ Unable to return before wiping out foes ♪

524
00:26:14,229 --> 00:26:22,723
♪ The Qiang flute wails over frosty land ♪

525
00:26:22,786 --> 00:26:34,700
♪ Some can’t sleep, others weep,
general’s hair turns gray ♪

526
00:26:48,980 --> 00:26:51,700
Yuanhao is heading south to Liupan Mountain

527
00:26:53,220 --> 00:26:55,060
to occupy Weizhou.

528
00:26:57,180 --> 00:26:58,940
= Ren Fu, courtesy name Youzhi =
If we cut off his supply of grains,

529
00:26:59,900 --> 00:27:01,500
he’ll have no choice

530
00:27:01,500 --> 00:27:02,700
but to head back.

531
00:27:03,740 --> 00:27:04,460
Then we can

532
00:27:04,460 --> 00:27:07,020
ambush him on the way.

533
00:27:08,780 --> 00:27:10,100
I, Ren Fu, can take up this task.

534
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:16,420
Go back to Guyuan to gather our troops.

535
00:27:17,180 --> 00:27:17,900
Ren Fu,

536
00:27:18,220 --> 00:27:19,220
lead them

537
00:27:20,100 --> 00:27:21,300
to tail the enemies.

538
00:27:22,540 --> 00:27:23,820
When the time is right,

539
00:27:24,100 --> 00:27:25,820
ambush them.

540
00:27:26,420 --> 00:27:27,180
- Yes. - Yes.

541
00:27:43,460 --> 00:27:43,980
Open the gate.

542
00:27:44,460 --> 00:27:45,180
Open the gate.

543
00:27:45,780 --> 00:27:46,540
= East Prosperity Gate =

544
00:27:49,900 --> 00:27:50,820
How did it go?

545
00:27:51,780 --> 00:27:53,940
General Ren Fu was misled by false information

546
00:27:54,540 --> 00:27:56,260
and trapped by Yuanhao’s troops.

547
00:27:57,020 --> 00:27:59,260
He refused to surrender after days of struggle

548
00:27:59,700 --> 00:28:02,380
and was killed along with

549
00:28:03,540 --> 00:28:04,540
thousands of soldiers.

550
00:28:08,540 --> 00:28:09,260
Ren Fu...

551
00:28:10,700 --> 00:28:11,660
died?

552
00:28:13,820 --> 00:28:15,500
Yesterday, after His Majesty read the report,

553
00:28:15,500 --> 00:28:17,140
he froze and sat there

554
00:28:17,180 --> 00:28:18,180
without eating or drinking anything.

555
00:28:18,180 --> 00:28:19,420
I was dismissed, too.

556
00:28:20,060 --> 00:28:21,020
When I saw him in the morning,

557
00:28:21,060 --> 00:28:22,420
he was still sitting there.

558
00:28:22,980 --> 00:28:24,500
He left with the report

559
00:28:24,620 --> 00:28:26,140
after getting changed

560
00:28:26,260 --> 00:28:27,060
and asked me

561
00:28:27,300 --> 00:28:28,300
not to follow him.

562
00:28:28,620 --> 00:28:29,820
He hasn’t come back yet.

563
00:28:30,740 --> 00:28:31,860
Today is his day off.

564
00:28:31,900 --> 00:28:33,140
I don’t know where he went.

565
00:28:42,020 --> 00:28:46,820
= The Tanguts died for their leader.
So did the Hans for our emperor. =

566
00:29:13,460 --> 00:29:14,340
Your Highness.

567
00:29:19,020 --> 00:29:20,460
Fan Zhongyan

568
00:29:21,220 --> 00:29:23,420
wrote this letter to Yuanhao six months ago.

569
00:29:24,340 --> 00:29:25,700
He advocates peace

570
00:29:26,780 --> 00:29:29,140
and wrote to Yuanhao to persuade him.

571
00:29:29,980 --> 00:29:31,220
He didn’t hide that

572
00:29:31,460 --> 00:29:33,300
and His Majesty never doubted him.

573
00:29:34,020 --> 00:29:37,500
Still, an investigation was conducted.

574
00:29:38,540 --> 00:29:41,700
That’s what the Imperial Security Agency does.

575
00:29:44,460 --> 00:29:45,420
I know.

576
00:29:46,980 --> 00:29:48,220
I can’t imagine

577
00:29:48,220 --> 00:29:49,940
how overwhelmed His Majesty was

578
00:29:51,820 --> 00:29:53,220
when he read this.

579
00:29:56,780 --> 00:29:58,540
His biggest fear is to see

580
00:29:59,780 --> 00:30:02,060
the innocent get killed.

581
00:30:02,980 --> 00:30:04,100
He isn’t blessed

582
00:30:05,780 --> 00:30:07,260
with a complete family,

583
00:30:08,580 --> 00:30:09,700
so the last thing he wants to see

584
00:30:09,700 --> 00:30:10,980
is the loss of family members.

585
00:30:14,660 --> 00:30:15,460
Your Highness,

586
00:30:16,820 --> 00:30:18,460
you should know

587
00:30:20,660 --> 00:30:22,420
where he went.

588
00:30:28,260 --> 00:30:29,020
That day,

589
00:30:29,900 --> 00:30:31,140
after he gave up the chance

590
00:30:31,140 --> 00:30:33,220
to pay respects to his mother at the Mausoleum,

591
00:30:34,340 --> 00:30:35,980
he went there and knelt for a whole night.

592
00:30:37,780 --> 00:30:38,740
Later on,

593
00:30:40,460 --> 00:30:42,780
when the news of Consort Li’s death came,

594
00:30:44,220 --> 00:30:46,100
he went there and knelt again.

595
00:30:47,580 --> 00:30:48,620
After that,

596
00:30:51,900 --> 00:30:53,660
Empress Dowager passed away.

597
00:30:54,460 --> 00:30:56,460
Again, he knelt

598
00:30:57,260 --> 00:30:58,420
for an entire night.

599
00:31:24,660 --> 00:31:25,420
Grandfather,

600
00:31:25,580 --> 00:31:26,220
father,

601
00:31:29,940 --> 00:31:30,820
I did my best.

602
00:31:33,460 --> 00:31:34,420
It’s not fair!

603
00:31:36,860 --> 00:31:38,380
I meant to achieve more,

604
00:31:39,460 --> 00:31:41,580
to stop the war with force,

605
00:31:44,620 --> 00:31:45,700
yet I failed.

606
00:31:53,300 --> 00:31:55,020
Had I taken Fan Zhongyan

607
00:31:55,020 --> 00:31:56,300
and Yan Shu’s advice

608
00:31:56,660 --> 00:31:57,780
to hold the position,

609
00:31:59,140 --> 00:32:01,540
Yuanhao would’ve caved eventually

610
00:32:01,540 --> 00:32:02,900
and bagged for a truce.

611
00:32:03,700 --> 00:32:04,500
Then

612
00:32:07,180 --> 00:32:09,100
so many warriors

613
00:32:09,140 --> 00:32:10,220
would’ve still been alive.

614
00:32:21,420 --> 00:32:22,860
How ironic!

615
00:32:24,900 --> 00:32:27,540
I only tolerated Yuanhao’s overreach

616
00:32:28,300 --> 00:32:29,780
and refused to resort to force in the past

617
00:32:29,780 --> 00:32:30,660
because I didn’t want to win

618
00:32:30,660 --> 00:32:32,140
at the cost of others’ lives.

619
00:32:34,020 --> 00:32:34,900
But now,

620
00:32:37,660 --> 00:32:39,300
all that’s left is shame

621
00:32:39,660 --> 00:32:40,660
despite the sacrifice

622
00:32:43,180 --> 00:32:44,540
of so many warriors.

623
00:33:10,500 --> 00:33:11,540
Oh, it’s you.

624
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:13,540
Who else could it be?

625
00:33:18,380 --> 00:33:19,540
I said earlier

626
00:33:21,900 --> 00:33:23,900
that whoever followed me would be killed.

627
00:33:25,260 --> 00:33:27,020
Don’t think I won’t.

628
00:33:27,900 --> 00:33:29,140
Don’t you remember

629
00:33:29,140 --> 00:33:30,500
that Huang Dehe was cut in half?

630
00:33:37,660 --> 00:33:38,900
Only you aren’t afraid of me.

631
00:33:41,420 --> 00:33:42,660
In this palace,

632
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:45,900
only you don’t fear me.

633
00:33:49,540 --> 00:33:50,540
You always do

634
00:33:50,540 --> 00:33:51,900
what you think is right

635
00:33:52,420 --> 00:33:54,300
and perform your role as you wish.

636
00:33:58,620 --> 00:34:00,140
You aren’t afraid of my anger

637
00:34:01,540 --> 00:34:03,020
or indifference.

638
00:34:03,020 --> 00:34:04,500
You aren’t afraid of being deposed

639
00:34:04,700 --> 00:34:05,700
or killed.

640
00:34:05,700 --> 00:34:07,020
I am afraid.

641
00:34:11,940 --> 00:34:13,100
But I know

642
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:18,060
you’ll never kill innocent people

643
00:34:19,500 --> 00:34:21,380
no matter how angry you are.

644
00:34:24,660 --> 00:34:26,380
You sentenced Huang Dehe to death

645
00:34:27,540 --> 00:34:29,300
to bring justice

646
00:34:29,540 --> 00:34:30,780
to General Liu Ping

647
00:34:30,780 --> 00:34:34,540
and those wronged and dead because of him.

648
00:34:54,940 --> 00:34:56,860
I never kill the innocent.

649
00:34:59,060 --> 00:35:00,620
Do I?

650
00:35:02,260 --> 00:35:03,540
It was my decision

651
00:35:03,580 --> 00:35:05,460
to battle Yuanhao’s force head-on

652
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:06,340
to end the war.

653
00:35:06,460 --> 00:35:07,220
I...

654
00:35:10,620 --> 00:35:11,380
Your Majesty.

655
00:35:12,660 --> 00:35:13,420
Servant!

656
00:35:13,540 --> 00:35:14,700
Call the Imperial Physicians!

657
00:35:21,580 --> 00:35:23,140
The Tanguts died

658
00:35:24,820 --> 00:35:27,540
for their leader.

659
00:35:28,460 --> 00:35:30,980
So did the Hans

660
00:35:31,660 --> 00:35:33,180
for our emperor.

661
00:35:36,900 --> 00:35:39,060
The brave and loyal sacrificed their lives.

662
00:35:40,460 --> 00:35:43,580
Their deaths will bring bad fortune to the state.

663
00:35:49,180 --> 00:35:50,940
Never kill the innocent?

664
00:35:52,420 --> 00:35:53,940
Never kill the innocent?

665
00:35:56,060 --> 00:35:56,940
You know,

666
00:35:56,940 --> 00:35:59,100
even a serial killer

667
00:35:59,820 --> 00:36:01,500
can only take dozens of lives

668
00:36:01,700 --> 00:36:02,940
throughout his life.

669
00:36:03,060 --> 00:36:03,820
Compared with that,

670
00:36:04,180 --> 00:36:05,300
those died in my hands are dozens of times more

671
00:36:05,420 --> 00:36:07,420
simply because I coveted the chance

672
00:36:07,460 --> 00:36:09,140
to have history remember

673
00:36:09,780 --> 00:36:11,700
my military achievement.

674
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:13,180
Your Majesty,

675
00:36:14,300 --> 00:36:15,060
you need to stop

676
00:36:15,060 --> 00:36:16,060
and have a rest.

677
00:36:17,180 --> 00:36:18,540
No one is perfect.

678
00:36:18,540 --> 00:36:20,220
We can only do our best to leave no regrets.

679
00:36:22,540 --> 00:36:23,420
Even if...

680
00:36:24,340 --> 00:36:26,180
Even if the state will be cursed

681
00:36:27,420 --> 00:36:28,540
with bad fortune,

682
00:36:31,460 --> 00:36:34,460
I’ll take the consequence with you.

683
00:36:35,820 --> 00:36:36,740
I’m not afraid.

684
00:36:46,340 --> 00:36:47,740
I’m sorry.

685
00:36:55,460 --> 00:36:56,380
Your Majesty.

686
00:37:00,340 --> 00:37:01,300
I am afraid.

687
00:37:06,980 --> 00:37:08,220
I’m afraid of losing you.

688
00:37:29,180 --> 00:37:30,700
Son!

689
00:37:32,208 --> 00:37:33,387
Come back!

690
00:37:33,460 --> 00:37:35,980
Come back, my son!

691
00:37:36,460 --> 00:37:40,100
- Son! - Come back!

692
00:37:40,740 --> 00:37:42,180
Son!

693
00:37:45,106 --> 00:37:46,678
Son!

694
00:37:50,140 --> 00:37:52,020
Son!

695
00:37:52,768 --> 00:37:53,968
Son!

696
00:37:55,220 --> 00:37:55,940
Son!

697
00:37:57,060 --> 00:37:59,700
You told me you’d achieve something big,

698
00:37:59,940 --> 00:38:01,860
then come back to marry

699
00:38:02,220 --> 00:38:04,060
and have babies.

700
00:38:05,460 --> 00:38:07,540
Where are you now?

701
00:38:07,540 --> 00:38:08,740
Where are you?

702
00:38:12,020 --> 00:38:14,700
Chief Han is back alive.

703
00:38:14,744 --> 00:38:16,240
Where are you?

704
00:38:28,180 --> 00:38:29,700
Is father getting better?

705
00:38:30,100 --> 00:38:32,100
Why can’t I visit him?

706
00:38:33,580 --> 00:38:34,580
I’m sure His Majesty

707
00:38:36,100 --> 00:38:37,340
is much better.

708
00:38:37,940 --> 00:38:39,340
Didn’t Her Highness say two days ago,

709
00:38:39,540 --> 00:38:41,300
that His Majesty would recover

710
00:38:41,620 --> 00:38:42,860
in a few days?

711
00:38:43,460 --> 00:38:44,660
But

712
00:38:45,540 --> 00:38:48,980
when brother taught me to write,

713
00:38:49,100 --> 00:38:52,500
I heard physicians saying

714
00:38:52,540 --> 00:38:54,980
father’s illness is severe.

715
00:38:54,980 --> 00:38:57,420
They’d puncture him with needles.

716
00:38:58,420 --> 00:39:00,340
I ran out to ask Her Highness

717
00:39:00,380 --> 00:39:03,340
but she told me repeatedly

718
00:39:03,420 --> 00:39:05,780
not to tell my mother

719
00:39:05,820 --> 00:39:08,220
because her baby will soon come out.

720
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:12,060
Two days ago, following Her Highness’ decree,

721
00:39:12,300 --> 00:39:13,420
I went to the Imperial Academy

722
00:39:13,460 --> 00:39:15,740
to have people copy content

723
00:39:16,340 --> 00:39:18,260
in Treatise on Causes and Symptoms of All Diseases

724
00:39:18,260 --> 00:39:20,420
= Ms. Xiu =
related to chest stuffiness and heartache.

725
00:39:20,860 --> 00:39:22,900
Deputy Officer Zhao at the Academy

726
00:39:23,340 --> 00:39:25,620
assigned the task to him.

727
00:39:25,980 --> 00:39:27,300
He finished it earlier today,

728
00:39:27,980 --> 00:39:29,700
so I brought him to report back to Her Highness.

729
00:39:30,620 --> 00:39:32,060
Her Highness just left

730
00:39:32,100 --> 00:39:32,980
to be with His Majesty in his chamber.

731
00:39:33,420 --> 00:39:35,180
She’s likely to stay the night there.

732
00:39:36,060 --> 00:39:37,460
Leave the copy here.

733
00:39:37,860 --> 00:39:38,940
I’ll report it to Her Highness

734
00:39:38,940 --> 00:39:40,140
once she comes back tomorrow.

735
00:39:40,660 --> 00:39:42,140
If she has further questions,

736
00:39:42,460 --> 00:39:43,780
you’ll be summoned.

737
00:40:15,620 --> 00:40:17,060
Father is ill.

738
00:40:18,380 --> 00:40:20,180
He’s so nice to me

739
00:40:20,900 --> 00:40:23,540
yet I can’t do anything for him

740
00:40:23,660 --> 00:40:26,260
when he’s in pain.

741
00:40:27,420 --> 00:40:29,540
Immortals, please help me.

742
00:40:29,660 --> 00:40:32,140
Pass father’s illness to me.

743
00:40:32,500 --> 00:40:33,860
I’m willing to bear twice,

744
00:40:34,180 --> 00:40:35,980
no, ten times

745
00:40:36,180 --> 00:40:38,900
the pain he’s suffering.

746
00:40:39,740 --> 00:40:44,100
Please help me.

747
00:40:44,380 --> 00:40:45,260
As long as...

748
00:40:46,100 --> 00:40:48,020
As long as father can get better,

749
00:40:48,740 --> 00:40:51,100
I’m willing

750
00:40:51,340 --> 00:40:52,740
to die.

751
00:41:14,420 --> 00:41:15,180
Who is there?

752
00:41:18,860 --> 00:41:20,620
A servant. I lost my way.

753
00:41:21,180 --> 00:41:21,900
Who is it?

754
00:41:25,140 --> 00:41:25,940
Who is there?

755
00:41:50,620 --> 00:41:55,580
= Xu Lantiao =

756
00:42:35,660 --> 00:42:36,620
As long as...

757
00:42:37,420 --> 00:42:39,380
As long as father can get better,

758
00:42:40,180 --> 00:42:42,460
I’m willing

759
00:42:42,660 --> 00:42:44,180
to die.

760
00:42:50,340 --> 00:42:53,660
Please bless that girl’s father

761
00:42:53,740 --> 00:42:54,940
to recover soon.

762
00:42:57,340 --> 00:42:59,220
His daughter is so sweet

763
00:42:59,820 --> 00:43:00,780
and loves him dearly.

764
00:43:03,140 --> 00:43:04,460
He must be

765
00:43:04,620 --> 00:43:07,420
a really nice person.

766
00:43:35,020 --> 00:43:38,140
♪ Isolated kite ♪

767
00:43:38,140 --> 00:43:41,220
♪ Left everything behind ♪

768
00:43:41,220 --> 00:43:44,540
♪ Lost soul ♪

769
00:43:44,540 --> 00:43:47,660
♪ Can’t feel cause he can’t love ♪

770
00:43:47,660 --> 00:43:50,780
♪ Fondness is a beam of light ♪

771
00:43:50,780 --> 00:43:53,900
♪ Shines in the dark ♪

772
00:43:53,940 --> 00:43:56,980
♪ That overshines stars ♪

773
00:43:57,020 --> 00:44:03,860
♪ And nourishes all living things ♪

774
00:44:04,580 --> 00:44:07,300
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

775
00:44:07,300 --> 00:44:11,300
♪ I don’t want to remember, but I can’t forget ♪

776
00:44:11,300 --> 00:44:17,340
♪ My hair turns grey too soon
Laughing at me for being so sentimental ♪

777
00:44:17,340 --> 00:44:20,020
♪ Those who love more are always hurt
by who love less ♪

778
00:44:20,020 --> 00:44:23,940
♪ I love you so much, and hope you are well ♪

779
00:44:23,940 --> 00:44:30,340
♪ Towards the direction of light ♪

780
00:44:30,340 --> 00:44:36,540
♪ Light it up for the people ♪

781
00:44:36,540 --> 00:44:42,700
♪ Cure the heartless injury ♪

